name: The 3rd International Conference on Innovation in Computer Science and Artificial Intelligence
content: The 3rd International Conference on Innovation in Computer Science and Artificial Intelligence on 23-25 October 2020 in Amsterdam, Netherlands aims to bring together academia, researchers, and scholars in order to exchange and share their experiences and research results about all aspects of specialized and interdisciplinary fields. This event provides an opportunity for all to network, share ideas, and also present their research work. In addition, discussion on the latest innovations, trends, and practical concerns and challenges faced in these fields are also encouraged.
